title: Google pixel 3a Xl Data transfer to 4a not working
content: I'm trying to transfer my data and copy everything to my new Google pixel 4A. the only problem with it is that the new 4A is asking for an old PIN number so that I can verify my Google account so that I can copy my data and I don't know what the 4a's pin was
